{"tid":447975,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[拔苗] 邊度跌低邊度起返身 Note 8 航班免費派","createTime":"2017-10-25T20:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T00:27:22.000Z","uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"070a825c2a716c4916af21baa610d47390500218","tid":447975,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T20:51:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/209365/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F209365%2F&d=mRKhycZ0hvTWpSKDX%2FBG%2F5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=b1912c88\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/209365/</a><br />\n<br />\n好受歡迎到要送電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港 Samsung 要學！邊度跌低邊度起返身 Note 8 航班免費派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-10/25/209365/uniqlo_1_c61f91218a2a8babf7d85fe4e541201b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-10%2F25%2F209365%2Funiqlo_1_c61f91218a2a8babf7d85fe4e541201b.jpg&h=06a46282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少人都講過，要克服失敗最重要係識得喺邊度跌低，就喺邊度起返身。如果識得加一點點自嘲，就算未必成功克服失敗，但至少會獲得一些掌聲和笑聲。版主口水多過浪花嘅鋪排，全因為 Samsung 喺西班牙送出咗<span style=\"color: red;\"> 200 部全新 </span>Galaxy Note 8 俾幸運嘅飛機乘客。<br />\n<br />\n去年因為<span style=\"color: red;\">電池爆炸</span>事故，Galaxy Note 7 被全球禁飛，呢件事相信 Samsung 未必想再提。偏偏他們西班牙分部卻冇有怕，日前在一班由馬德里飛往加利西亞的內陸航班，向 200 名乘客免費派發 Galaxy Note 8。當時一些睡眼惺忪的乘客收到空姐派發的手機十分驚喜，手機包裝上寫著<span style=\"color: red;\">「一年前我們要求你將手機關上，現在我們歡迎你登機」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-10/25/209365/uniqlo_1_64ba0fe4908294eff5549f3903670d64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-10%2F25%2F209365%2Funiqlo_1_64ba0fe4908294eff5549f3903670d64.jpg&h=0552388d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，就是邊度跌低邊度起返身。今次推廣是 Samsung 西班牙跟航空公司 Iberia Airlines 的合作，而雙方的高層亦在航班上，這公關 Show 很快就在網上流傳，不知道香港 Samsung 又會否有樣學樣呢？"},{"pid":"1b74afcc3b84a540cd6c61092268d849be1d79ba","tid":447975,"uid":73356,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:17:47.000Z","msg":"全球有香港都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0573f941309cc6d9475027194cbe401ae2f715","tid":447975,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:38:15.000Z","msg":"宣傳手法層出不窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0193043953926fac11ce25e7d6ac5ef9357631eb","tid":447975,"uid":92477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:58:48.000Z","msg":"香港代理一見好賣<br />\n連note fans優惠都提早cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eb67e1172869439d688d6ae9250ec0f041188f","tid":447975,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:03:22.000Z","msg":"港豬只配俾1700整番個mon"},{"pid":"178b41652a73b1311ab4ff312d9d82d4118137db","tid":447975,"uid":5297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:30:04.000Z","msg":"恐怖襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送200部炸彈上機"},{"pid":"5a948d5f02f896e968532a905575118328167b9b","tid":447975,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T23:39:30.000Z","msg":"香港三星分部真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d62f6493a5c615354e8c115043b6d250d361d2","tid":447975,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:27:22.000Z","msg":"香港會派$100蚊note 8 coupon(只限同Shamesung 正價購買)"}]}